Acheroxenylla lipsae Palacios-Vargas, 2020
( Collembola , Poduromorpha , Hypogastruridae ), and the catfish
Astroblepus riberae (Cardona and Guerao, 1994)
(Actinopterygii, Siluriformes , Astroblepidae ) are known (Cardona and Guerao, 1994;
). Thus, the present work describes the third troglobitic species and the first troglobitic terrestrial isopod for the country.

